OL,3,CShip captain's claim of mechanical
OL,4,Cfailure before fatal crash ruled out
OL,6,FIn a closing speech on Thursday,
OL,7,Fprosecutor Julia Faure Walker rejected
OL,8,Fhis claims and suggested Motin had
OL,9,Flied about what happened to "get back
OL,10,Fto his wife" in Russia.
OL,12,FShe cast doubt that the experienced
OL,13,Fmariner was "unable to press a button"
OL,14,Fto switch from autopilot to manual
OL,15,Fsteering.
