OL,3,CShip captain's claim of mechanical
OL,4,Cfailure before fatal crash ruled out
OL,6,F"There were no mechanical or
OL,7,Felectronic difficulties on the Solong.
OL,8,FThe rudder was working. The only thing
OL,9,Fthat was not working on the 10th March
OL,10,F2025 was the man in the dock."
OL,12,FThe prosecutor suggested jurors may
OL,13,Fconclude that Motin had a "lax
OL,14,Fattitude" and "thought he knew better
OL,15,Fthan anyone else".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
