OL,3,CShip captain's claim of mechanical
OL,4,Cfailure before fatal crash ruled out
OL,6,FShe pointed to the fact that he had
OL,7,Fswitched off the Solong's bridge
OL,8,Fnavigation watch alert system (BNWAS),
OL,9,Fwhich was designed to ensure there is
OL,10,Fsomeone physically on the bridge and
OL,11,Fawake.
OL,13,FShe told jurors: "He kept the door
OL,14,Fshut, kept the bridge door shut and
OL,15,Fkept you from being able to see what
OL,16,Freally happened.
OL,18,F"He does not want you to look inside
OL,19,Fand see the reality of his failure to
OL,20,Fkeep a proper lookout."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
