OL,3,CShip captain's claim of mechanical
OL,4,Cfailure before fatal crash ruled out
OL,6,FMs Faure Walker said the collision
OL,7,Fposed a "serious and obvious risk to
OL,8,Fthe crew", she said.
OL,10,FAnd it was "foreseeable" that Mr
OL,11,FPernia would be on the bow greasing as
OL,12,Fpart of his job when the Solong
OL,13,Fsmashed into the side of Stena
OL,14,FImmaculate, causing a massive
OL,15,Fexplosion.
OL,17,FMs Faure-Walker said Motin was
OL,18,Fresponsible for "multiple failures"
OL,19,Fthat caused Mr Pernia's death.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
