OL,3,CShip captain's claim of mechanical
OL,4,Cfailure before fatal crash ruled out
OL,6,FHe allegedly failed to sound the
OL,7,Falarm, summon help or initiate a crash
OL,8,Fstop and should have acted sooner to
OL,9,Fsteer the Solong away from its
OL,10,Fcollision course, jurors heard.
OL,12,FWhether in isolation or combination,
OL,13,FMs Faure Walker said the defendant's
OL,14,Ffailures were so "exceptionally bad
OL,15,Fthey amount to gross negligence."
OL,17,FMotin, from Primorsky, St Petersburg,
OL,18,Fhas denied gross negligence
OL,19,Fmanslaughter and the Old Bailey trial
OL,20,Fcontinues.
